# Home Assistant Add-on: MooseFS

[![Release][release-shield]][release] ![Project Stage][project-stage-shield]

Mount a MooseFS share from Home Assistant and expose the MooseFS GUI through
Home Assistant Ingress.

## About

This add-on builds MooseFS from upstream source, starts the MooseFS GUI in the
container, and runs a supervised `mfsmount` loop that can keep retrying without
taking down the rest of the add-on.

The default mount path is `/share/moosefs` so the mounted tree can be shared
with the Home Assistant host when the underlying bind mount propagation allows
it.

